{"text_id":126544,"tokens":["How"," to"," Play"," Basketball",":"," A"," Comprehensive"," Guide","\n\n","Basketball"," is"," a"," fun"," and"," exciting"," sport"," that"," can"," be"," enjoyed"," both"," indoors"," and"," outdoors","."," Whether"," you"," are"," playing"," with"," friends"," or"," in"," a"," league",","," the"," rules"," of"," basketball"," are"," fairly"," simple"," to"," learn","."," In"," this"," article",","," we"," will"," cover"," the"," basics"," of"," how"," to"," play"," basketball",","," from"," the"," equipment"," you"," need"," to"," the"," skills"," you"," need"," to"," practice",".","\n\n","Get"," a"," Ball"," and"," a"," Hoop","\n\n","Before"," you"," can"," start"," playing"," basketball",","," you"," will"," need"," a"," ball"," and"," a"," hoop","."," Most"," basketball","s"," are"," made"," of"," leather"," or"," synthetic"," materials"," and"," come"," in"," different"," sizes",","," depending"," on"," your"," age"," and"," skill"," level","."," You"," can"," find"," basketball"," hoops"," at"," most"," sports"," stores"," or"," online",","," and"," they"," come"," in"," a"," variety"," of"," sizes",","," from"," portable"," to"," stationary",".","\n\n","Break"," Into"," Two"," Teams","\n\n","Basketball"," is"," a"," game"," that"," is"," played"," with"," two"," teams",","," each"," consisting"," of"," five"," players","."," The"," objective"," of"," the"," game"," is"," to"," score"," more"," points"," than"," your"," opponent"," by"," shooting"," the"," ball"," through"," the"," hoop",".","\n\n","Score"," Points"," by"," Shooting"," the"," Ball"," Through"," the"," Hoop","\n\n","The"," most"," important"," part"," of"," playing"," basketball"," is"," scoring"," points","."," You"," can"," score"," points"," by"," shooting"," the"," ball"," through"," the"," hoop",","," or"," by"," getting"," fou","led"," and"," making"," free"," throws",".","\n\n","Move"," the"," Ball"," by"," Dri","bbling"," or"," Passing","\n\n","To"," move"," the"," ball"," down"," the"," court",","," you"," can"," dri","bble"," it"," or"," pass"," it","."," Dri","bbling"," is"," when"," you"," bounce"," the"," ball"," with"," your"," fingertips",","," while"," passing"," is"," when"," you"," throw"," the"," ball"," to"," a"," teammate",".","\n\n","Stand"," Correct","ly","\n\n","When"," you"," are"," dri","bbling"," or"," shooting",","," it"," is"," important"," to"," stand"," correctly","."," You"," should"," have"," your"," feet"," shoulder","-","width"," apart",","," with"," your"," knees"," slightly"," bent"," and"," your"," weight"," evenly"," distributed",".","\n\n","Bounce"," the"," Ball"," with"," Your"," Finger","tips","\n\n","When"," you"," are"," dri","bbling"," the"," ball",","," you"," should"," use"," your"," fingertips"," to"," control"," it","."," This"," will"," help"," you"," maintain"," control"," of"," the"," ball"," and"," move"," it"," quickly"," down"," the"," court",".","\n\n","Try"," to"," Keep"," the"," Ball"," About"," Waist","-","High","\n\n","When"," you"," are"," dri","bbling"," the"," ball",","," you"," should"," try"," to"," keep"," it"," about"," waist","-","high","."," This"," will"," help"," you"," protect"," the"," ball"," and"," make"," it"," harder"," for"," your"," opponent"," to"," steal"," it",".","\n\n","Keep"," Your"," Head"," Up","\n\n","When"," you"," are"," dri","bbling"," the"," ball",","," you"," should"," keep"," your"," head"," up"," and"," look"," around"," you","."," This"," will"," help"," you"," see"," where"," your"," teammates"," are"," and"," where"," your"," opponents"," are",".","\n\n","Start"," Moving"," When"," You","'","re"," Ready","\n\n","When"," you"," are"," ready"," to"," move"," down"," the"," court",","," you"," should"," start"," moving","."," You"," can"," move"," by"," dri","bbling"," the"," ball"," or"," passing"," it"," to"," a"," teammate",".","\n\n","Practice"," Dri","bbling"," with"," Both"," Hands","\n\n","To"," become"," a"," better"," dri","bbler",","," you"," should"," practice"," dri","bbling"," with"," both"," hands","."," This"," will"," help"," you"," become"," more"," versatile"," and"," make"," it"," harder"," for"," your"," opponent"," to"," predict"," your"," moves",".","\n\n","Practice"," Making"," Different"," Kinds"," of"," Passes","\n\n","To"," become"," a"," better"," passer",","," you"," should"," practice"," making"," different"," kinds"," of"," passes","."," This"," will"," help"," you"," learn"," how"," to"," pass"," the"," ball"," quickly"," and"," accurately",".","\n\n","Square"," Up"," with"," the"," Basket"," Each"," Time"," You"," Shoot","\n\n","When"," you"," are"," ready"," to"," shoot"," the"," ball",","," you"," should"," square"," up"," with"," the"," basket","."," This"," will"," help"," you"," aim"," more"," accurately"," and"," make"," it"," easier"," to"," score"," points",".","\n\n","Balance"," the"," Ball"," on"," Your"," Dominant"," Hand","\n\n","When"," you"," are"," dri","bbling"," or"," shooting",","," you"," should"," balance"," the"," ball"," on"," your"," dominant"," hand","."," This"," will"," help"," you"," control"," the"," ball"," better"," and"," make"," it"," harder"," for"," your"," opponent"," to"," steal"," it",".","\n\n","Roll"," the"," Ball"," Off"," Your"," Hand","\n\n","When"," you"," are"," shooting"," the"," ball",","," you"," should"," roll"," it"," off"," your"," hand","."," This"," will"," help"," you"," maintain"," control"," of"," the"," ball"," and"," increase"," your"," accuracy",".","\n\n","Push"," Off"," with"," Your"," Feet",","," Jumping"," Straight"," Up","\n\n","When"," you"," are"," ready"," to"," shoot"," the"," ball",","," you"," should"," push"," off"," with"," your"," feet"," and"," jump"," straight"," up","."," This"," will"," help"," you"," get"," more"," height"," and"," increase"," your"," chances"," of"," scoring"," points",".","\n\n","Aim"," for"," an"," Imagin","ary"," Dime"," on"," the"," Lip"," of"," the"," Rim","\n\n","When"," you"," are"," shooting"," the"," ball",","," you"," should"," aim"," for"," an"," imaginary"," dime"," on"," the"," lip"," of"," the"," rim","."," This"," will"," help"," you"," aim"," more"," accurately"," and"," make"," it"," easier"," to"," score"," points",".","\n\n","Practice"," Lay","-","Ups"," from"," Both"," Sides","\n\n","To"," become"," a"," better"," scorer",","," you"," should"," practice"," lay","-","ups"," from"," both"," sides","."," This"," will"," help"," you"," become"," more"," versatile"," and"," make"," it"," harder"," for"," your"," opponent"," to"," predict"," your"," moves",".","\n\n","Shoot"," Const","antly",","," from"," Everywhere","\n\n","To"," become"," a"," better"," shooter",","," you"," should"," shoot"," constantly"," from"," everywhere","."," This"," will"," help"," you"," develop"," your"," accuracy"," and"," make"," it"," easier"," to"," score"," points",".","\n\n","Learn"," Your"," Role"," on"," Defense","\n\n","To"," become"," a"," better"," defender",","," you"," should"," learn"," your"," role"," on"," defense","."," This"," will"," help"," you"," know"," where"," to"," position"," yourself"," and"," how"," to"," prevent"," your"," opponent"," from"," scoring"," points",".","\n\n","Learn"," the"," Correct"," Defensive"," St","ance","\n\n","When"," you"," are"," playing"," defense",","," you"," should"," have"," the"," correct"," defensive"," stance","."," This"," includes"," keeping"," your"," feet"," shoulder","-","width"," apart",","," your"," knees"," bent",","," and"," your"," weight"," balanced",".","\n\n","Practice"," Your"," Side","-","to","-","Side"," Movements","\n\n","To"," become"," a"," better"," defender",","," you"," should"," practice"," your"," side","-","to","-","side"," movements","."," This"," will"," help"," you"," stay"," in"," front"," of"," your"," opponent"," and"," prevent"," them"," from"," getting"," past"," you",".","\n\n","Stay"," on"," Your"," Feet"," as"," Much"," as"," Possible","\n\n